snippet.title: Trailer Super Vadimka VI: A Terrible Threat there is No Vadimka (2023)
snippet.description: Super Vadimka VI: A Terrible Threat there is No Vadimka - the sixth and final part of the action and horror that was announced on January 5, 2023 about the adventures of an asshole from Velizh named Vadim Kulev aka Super Vadimka, he is considered a legend. Practically, the game is a 16-bit version in the style of the SNES masterpiece and contains about 100 levels and complex bloodthirsty bosses practically infected from.  Kulechkophobia contributing to the disease for the attack of the main character.
